Package au.edu.anu.twapps.mm

Interface IMMModel

All Superinterfaces:
Originator
All Known Implementing Classes:
MMModel
public interface IMMModel extends Originator
Author:
Ian Davies - 10 Jan. 2019

Interface implemented by MMModel is part of the Model-View-Controller pattern.

This interface extends Originator as part of the Momento pattern to restore model state as part of the undo/redo system.

  • Method Details

    • canClose

      boolean canClose()
      Query to ask the user to confirm closing an open Project.

      Returns:
      true if confirmed (file is saved or user does not want the file saved) and false if user cancels the operation.

    • doNewProject

      void doNewProject​(String proposedName, fr.cnrs.iees.graph.impl.TreeGraph<fr.cnrs.iees.graph.impl.TreeGraphDataNode,​fr.cnrs.iees.graph.impl.ALEdge> templateGraph, InputStream archiveStream)
      Actions required when creating a new Project. The parameters are supplied from the LibraryTable.

      Parameters:
      proposedName - Default name of the project.
      templateGraph - Project graph from the model.
      archiveStream - Project artifacts (may be null).
